snippet.textDisplay: A really nice reworking by the talented Sahir Ali Bagga of Begum Akhtar's sublime original. Bagga comes closest in Pakistan to AR Rahman's musical ear and versatile style. Unlike this week's "Ranjish hee Sahi" effort this is a good selection from an old master adapted for the modern sound of Coke Studio.
